1009
01:14:08,311 --> 01:14:10,643
"who were in my English class last year.

1010
01:14:10,747 --> 01:14:13,648
"And it hits me, Mrs. Gruwell,

1011
01:14:13,750 --> 01:14:16,014
"my crazy English teacher from last year,

1012
01:14:16,119 --> 01:14:18,781
