1015
01:14:26,062 --> 01:14:31,022
"l receive my schedule and the first teacher is Mrs. Gruwell in Room 203.

1016
01:14:31,368 --> 01:14:34,504
"l walk into the room and feel as though

1017
01:14:34,505 --> 01:14:38,134
