1029
01:15:29,194 --> 01:15:32,823
"Victoria, it's not every day one finds an African-American student

1030
01:15:32,931 --> 01:15:36,799
"in A.P. and honors courses." As if I didn't notice.

1031
01:15:36,902 --> 01:15:39,302
