01:42:34,964 --> 01:42:38,229
At 2:00 today, my brother was given a verdict on his own trial.

1336
01:42:38,368 --> 01:42:40,996
No O.J. Dream Team, just a court-appointed attorney

1337
01:42:41,137 --> 01:42:43,105
