It just means somebody pays for the crime.

1342
01:43:00,924 --> 01:43:02,448
So, you got time now?

1343
01:43:09,333 --> 01:43:10,925
Anyone know where Andre's been?

1344
01:43:11,068 --> 01:43:12,330
I haven't seen him on the bus.

1345
01:43:12,469 --> 01:43:13,936
Yeah, I haven't talked to him either.

1346
01:43:22,846 --> 01:43:24,370
Ms. G?

1347
01:43:24,748 --> 01:43:27,080
Are we gonna have this same room next year, again?

1348
