1349
01:43:31,855 --> 01:43:33,379
What do you mean?

1350
01:43:33,490 --> 01:43:36,186
Well, I teach freshman and sophomore years.

1351
01:43:36,293 --> 01:43:39,421
You mean, we're not gonna be with you next year?

1352
01:43:42,133 --> 01:43:43,498
Well, l...

1353
01:43:45,370 --> 01:43:49,101
I don't teach juniors. I thought you guys understood that.

1354
01:43:49,608 --> 01:43:50,734
What? What are you talking about?

1355
01:43:52,944 --> 01:43:54,571
You don't wanna be our teacher next year?

