I can't believe I'm getting divorced.

1383
01:45:20,701 --> 01:45:23,135
I never thought this would happen.

1384
01:45:27,107 --> 01:45:29,200
What do I do now?

1385
01:45:30,178 --> 01:45:32,646
Next year, I won't even have my kids.

1386
01:45:33,047 --> 01:45:35,345
You think you should stay with them?

1387
01:45:36,217 --> 01:45:38,515
Or is it better they move on?

1388
01:45:38,853 --> 01:45:40,320
I don't know.

1389
01:45:44,125 --> 01:45:46,593
It's just a job, like you said.

1390
01:45:46,694 --> 01:45:48,321
Yeah, it is.

1391
01:45:49,263 --> 01:45:51,231
But is the job finished?

1392
01:45:53,568 --> 01:45:55,160
Listen to me now.

1393
01:45:55,436 --> 01:45:57,961
What you've done with those kids...

