01:46:00,375 --> 01:46:02,673
I don't even have words for it.

1395
01:46:04,413 --> 01:46:09,373
But one thing's for sure, you are an amazing teacher.

1396
01:46:11,253 --> 01:46:12,618
Special.

1397
01:46:13,389 --> 01:46:17,792
You have been blessed with a burden, my daughter.

1398
01:46:19,762 --> 01:46:21,730
And I envy you that.

1399
01:46:24,433 --> 01:46:26,060
And I admire you.

1400
01:46:28,570 --> 01:46:32,563
And how many fathers ever get to say that to their daughters

1401
01:46:32,708 --> 01:46:34,676
and really mean it?

1402
01:46:38,547 --> 01:46:41,641
