01:47:52,491 --> 01:47:54,857
in the curriculum for her to teach.

1431
01:47:55,494 --> 01:47:59,157
Unless Brian trades one of his junior classes for a sophomore.

1432
01:47:59,264 --> 01:48:00,322
No.

1433
01:48:02,100 --> 01:48:04,330
Then there's nothing I can do.

1434
01:48:07,873 --> 01:48:09,170
So that's it?

1435
01:48:10,308 --> 01:48:11,775
Believe it or not, Ms. Gruwell,

1436
01:48:11,877 --> 01:48:14,607
