I heard about your brother's conviction. I'm sorry.

1453
01:49:27,187 --> 01:49:29,382
Is that why you've missed class so much?

1454
01:49:29,489 --> 01:49:31,286
I had things to do.

1455
01:49:34,561 --> 01:49:36,358
About this.

1456
01:49:36,830 --> 01:49:37,990
The evaluation assignment

1457
01:49:38,099 --> 01:49:39,566
was to grade yourself on the work you're doing.

1458
01:49:39,667 --> 01:49:42,101
